   Purpose     : Global Settings â€” Buttons showcase page (KI-Admin style).
                 Displays all button variants as static live demos using the
                 ButtonDemoCard component. Each card has an independently
                 toggled code-snippet section. No token logic or DB writes.
                 Token editing is at /global-settings/buttons/edit.
   ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
   Changes     :
     - 1.0.0  2026-03-26  Initial implementation (Phase 1 placeholder).
     - 2.0.0  2026-05-12  Phase B: token editor (moved to /edit in Phase C).
